high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room and turn right to face the black table.
Pick up the knife on the black table on the counter.
Look up to face the apple on the black table.
Cut the apple on the black table into three pieces.
Turn left to face the white table.
Place the knife on the white table.
Turn to the right to face the apple on the black table.
Pick up a piece of apple on the black table.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and remove it.
Look down to face the table the microwave is on.
Place the apple piece on the table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple plus place it on the microwave stand.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go across the kitchen, turn right at the white table, then go to the black stand across from you.
Pick up the butter knife underneath the lettuce, on the black stand.
Move closer to the black stand in front of you.
Cut the apple in the back left corner of the black stand.
Turn to the white table to your left.
Place the knife on the table, in front of the bread.
Turn to your right, back to the black stand.
Pick up one of the apple slices on the back, left corner of the stand.
Turn around and walk to the stove, then turn left and go across the room to the microwave in the right corner of the room.
Place the apple slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the apple from the microwave.
Step back from the microwave.
Put the apple slice on the front, right corner of the table the microwave is on.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple on the microwave table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the shelves in the corner.
Pick up a knife on the shelves.
Turn and go to the shelves in the corner.
Cut the apple on the shelves.
Turn and go to the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Turn and go to the shelves in the corner.
Pick up a slice of apple on the shelves.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the table in the corner.
Put the slice of apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of apple on the table in the corner.
